f rape and introduced the death penalty for repeat offenders and cases causing death.\n    *   **Relevance:** Demonstrates the judicial application of murder provisions in cases of extreme brutality and its role in legislative reform.\n\n---\n\nThis report provides a comprehensive overview of IPC Section 302 and related legal aspects. Should you require further clarification or specific legal guidance, please consult with a legal professional.",
